## 4. Build and upload

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install --upgrade setuptools wheel build twine
```

Build the package (wheel and sdist)
```bash
python -m build 
```

Ensure `.pypirc` in user folder is correct, then upload
```bash
twine upload dist/*
```
